# INTRODUCTION

# ZeroWaste aids users in avoiding distractions as you work on your job or tasks. It is an application that allows you to choose 
when distractions, such as social media, messaging with friends, or entertainment, become limited with a push of a button.

# USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

# 1. Press Start button
# 2. Select application that you'd want locked/disabled.
# 3. Set time to how long you want app to be locked/disabled for.
# 4. Timer starts, user can press "Unlock" button to manually unlock application.
# 5. Settings icon on top right allowing user to manage settings (EX: Choosing Alarm Sound, Creating PIN, Send Feedback).

# RELEVANT INFORMATION

# ZeroWaste can run on ANY Android device (Utilizes Android KitKat).
